Introduction

Seori is a Korean R&B/Soul singer based in South Korea. On May, 12th, 2020, Seori released her first EP album [?depacse ohw] with the Label ATISPAUS and all the songs in this album were written and composed by Seori.

From a young age, she was heavily influenced by various artists including Coldplay, Avril Lavigne, Paramore and G-Dragon and started to compose her own songs when she was just 16 years old. Many of her songs touch on people’s feeling of loneliness and isolation, which is something rather hard to express in words.
